Game ......: Resident Evil Code Veronica
Date ...: 2003.11.10
Video ..: PAL
Ripped by .: DCP
Rip notes .: nothing removed

After narrowly surviving the horrific onslaught in Raccoon City, Claire 
Redfield now seeks clues in search of  her missing brother, Chris. The Umbrella corporation memo read : " Confidential : phase 1 - Raccoon City. 
Test complete. Phase 2 - Paris Facility. Fully operational. " 
 
To her horror, she discovers Umbrella's insidious activities aren't isolated to 
 the remote, mid-western city. No. Something much larger is going on here. 
 
Flesh-eating zombies, horrific beasts and even stranger mutations have spread to a global scale! Just how far this twisted conspiration extend ? What is Umbrella really up to ? And who is the bio-tech terror?